headline: 3 Reasons to Sell TMO and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the last six months, Thermo Fisher shares have sunk to $508.90, producing a disappointing 17.1% loss - worse than the S&P 500’s 1.2% drop. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
